Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:14.97,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:15.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:23.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:26.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:30.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:33.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:36.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:51.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:54.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:59.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:02.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:11.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:15.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:18.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.67,0:01:22.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In their quest for\Nworld domination,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:26.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker created a new\Ncyborg, Dokugander,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:29.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but the Kamen Rider defeated\Nit in valiant combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:34.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But then, Dokugander sealed\Nitself inside a giant cocoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:37.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and disappeared without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:44.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker had already disposed of Professor\NKoizumi, who had learned their secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:48.73,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(447.167,200.389)}Dokugander
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:48.73,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,660.389)}Battle at Osaka Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:56.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H466B69&\3c&H1A170A&}Hanshin University of Science
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yoshioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really find a man-sized\Ncaterpillar at the base of Mount Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true? Do you have proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have pictures, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, would you?\NWe're on a deadline, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, now.\NI'll bring them soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The pictures I left\Non my desk are gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I got lost on the way back\Nand couldn't get in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...\NI felt sure that you were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Bring us those pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll speak to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen. Yoshioka here\Nsaid he saw a man-sized
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,caterpillar near the base of Mount\NFuji, but he was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But he just said\Nhe had pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a publicity stunt. He's just\Ntrying to get his name into the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please!\NI really did see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns out Professor\NKoizumi is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Assistant Professor Yoshioka\NDriven From Hanshin University."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"The groundless rumors about a giant\Ncaterpillar was a publicity stunt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to get his name out\Nin the newspapers."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw the caterpillar\Nourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that Professor\NKoizumi is an impostor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Yoshioka is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A drug I've been researching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a growth serum that accelerates\Nthe development of cocoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A growth serum?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind coming by my\Nlaboratory to investigate further?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a secret laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll help me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have returned to life...\Nand this time, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just feeling\Nyou out this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders from FBI headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They think Shocker's\Nplanning something in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 45 kilometers left!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yoshioka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's too late, Ichimonji Hayato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yoshioka is already\Nin our custody.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you tried\Nto delay our arrival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Precisely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is nothing that\NShocker cannot do!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You do research in\Na place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!\NWhat is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now explain the\Nwork I'll have you doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen\Nsuch big cocoons...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Each contains a new\Ncyborg created by Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But it will take several\Nmonths for them to develop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We require these cyborgs\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want\Nme to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that cocoon growth\Nserum you invented
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to make them fully-grown\NDokuganders as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Yoshioka...\Nlook carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We can kidnap your daughter\Nany time we choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think it over carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:53.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&H38304F&\fs60\an9}Yoshioka
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're terribly\Nsorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the paper goods exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll trade old newspapers and\Nmagazines for toilet paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this is\NHayato's "big job" for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Paper exchange in Osaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no job for a young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have stayed home\Nlike Michi and Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you really think\NShocker will be after Miki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking Miki hostage is the best way\Nto threaten Mr. Yoshioka, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. A suspicious vehicle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad. It's a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father was in an accident.\NHe's been taken to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Child... you tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! You can't fool me!\NStupid rotten lousy jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like you guys at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me the ego trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's take him to Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your base?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Mr. Yoshioka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You want another karate chop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:10:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with the feminism.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:11:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki needs your attention first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll play with you, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,\NI'll save your papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Butt out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Us kids are in this together.\NRight, Miki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Burned...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet down, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop selling out your\Nfriends for points.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Mr. Yoshioka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, take care of Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's some monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster! Come down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot escape me any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. But we should check on\Nthe others back in the apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:30.10,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working!\NI can't find my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like I told you!\NOsaka is big!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never find your father\Nwith some little kid's telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mean.\NThis is why I hate boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Mr. Photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a girl\Nwith a red ribbon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and a very snotty-looking\Nlittle boy nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Goro and\NMiki could have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly hope Shocker\Ndidn't get them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker is more likely\Nto get the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, do you know about Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's the Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I got so worried,\NI came rushing right from Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye of little faith, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Pretty good way to\Nkeep tabs on Shocker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. How about a picture\Nto remember this by?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This place belongs to Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't start crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll make me cry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare the women and\Nchildren, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of coward\Nwould torture a child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You will all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really how I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshioka has completed\Nthe cocoon growth serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Pull out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a move on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So there was an entrance\Nhere, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the growth serum, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to work at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yoshioka, don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Something terrible will\Nhappen if you do. Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll kill him off later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Mr. Yoshioka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford\Nfurther interruptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a chemical formula\Nfor dissolving cocoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be making\Nany more cyborgs now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's some kind of signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have Taki in\Nan underground cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll save you soon. Rider."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he'd come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! I'm glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dokugander...\NIt's finally time to end you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my daughter all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NWe have her somewhere safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't outrun me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come visit me in Tokyo some\Ntime, okay, Miki?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come back to\NOsaka some time too, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.87,0:22:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What, not us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Us kids are in it together.\NAdults can butt out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, bye-bye! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.64,0:22:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See you. Take care, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't Hayato and Taki be\Ntaking the plane back to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, they don't trust something\Nmade out of steel to really fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:22:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Motorbikes are\Nmore their speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to be leaving\Nthose wild women behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,\Nlet's take a drive to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:19.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The battle was over,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:23.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but with Shocker still\Naiming for world domination,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.57,0:23:27.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,they would surely send more\Ncyborgs to Japan in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.37,0:23:33.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In that moment, Ichimonji Hayato\Nrenewed his pledge to fight Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:40.50,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,510)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:42.64,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:42.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.64,0:23:44.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:46.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous\Nmerman, Amazonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:50.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The terrifying fish-man Amazonia\Nseeks uranium on the ocean floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:53.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider will fight a steaming\Nmidsummer battle near the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:23:56.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Prepare for thrills, suspense,\Nand underwater action!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:24:00.77,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,690.389)}Monstrous Merman Amazonia
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:24:00.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for\N"Monstrous Merman Amazonia."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:10.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:13.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.39,0:24:15.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:18.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.89,0:24:20.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.77,0:24:22.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:24.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.44,0:24:25.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.23,0:24:28.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.32,0:24:33.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.99,0:24:37.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.58,0:24:41.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.67,0:24:45.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dokugander,\NBattle at Osaka Castle!"